Bradley Wiggins and Dave Brailsford are awarded knighthoods in the 2013 New Year Honours list, while Sarah Storey becomes a Dame, the female equivalent of a knight. (The Guardian) (The Daily Telegraph) (Road.cc)In Formula One, Sebastian Vettel wins the 2013 Bahrain Grand Prix ahead of Kimi Räikkönen and Romain Grosjean. (BBC) (The Guardian)